---
import SmartSteuerPromo from '~/components/common/SmartSteuerPromo.astro';
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Hero from '~/components/widgets/Hero.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'SmartSteuer - Best German Tax Declaration Software',
  description:
    "Discover SmartSteuer, Germany's leading online tax declaration platform. Learn how this user-friendly software can simplify your German tax filing and maximize your refund.",
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero
    tagline="SmartSteuer"
    title="Best German Tax Declaration Software"
    subtitle="Discover SmartSteuer, one of Germany's leading online tax declaration platforms. Learn how this user-friendly software can simplify your German tax filing and maximize your refund."
  />

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div
      class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert animate-in fade-in duration-700 delay-100 data-[intersection]:animate-in"
    >
      <h2>Why Choose SmartSteuer?</h2>
      <h3>1. User-Friendly Interface</h3>
      <p>
        SmartSteuer features an intuitive, step-by-step guidance system that walks you through the entire tax
        declaration process. You don't need to be a tax expert – the software asks you simple questions in plain
        language and automatically fills in the correct forms based on your answers.
      </p>

      <h3>2. Maximize Your Tax Refund</h3>
      <p>
        The average tax refund in Germany is around €1,000, but many people miss out on deductions they're entitled to.
        SmartSteuer's intelligent system identifies all possible deductions and tax-saving opportunities specific to
        your situation, including:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Work-related expenses (Werbungskosten)</li>
        <li>Commuting costs (Pendlerpauschale)</li>
        <li>Home office deductions</li>
        <li>Professional development and training</li>
        <li>Moving costs for work-related relocations</li>
        <li>Childcare expenses</li>
        <li>Health insurance and additional insurance premiums</li>
        <li>Donations and charitable contributions</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>3. Automatic Data Import</h3>
      <p>
        SmartSteuer can automatically import your tax data from previous years and retrieve pre-filled information from
        German tax authorities, saving you valuable time and reducing errors.
      </p>

      <h3>4. ELSTER Integration</h3>
      <p>
        SmartSteuer is fully integrated with ELSTER (Elektronische Steuererklärung), the official electronic tax filing
        system of the German tax authorities. This means you can submit your tax declaration directly to the Finanzamt
        (tax office) electronically – no printing, signing, or mailing required.
      </p>

      <h3>5. Expert Support Available</h3>
      <p>
        If you have questions or need assistance, SmartSteuer offers various support options, including detailed help
        articles, video tutorials, and customer service to guide you through tricky tax situations.
      </p>

      <h2>Who Should Use SmartSteuer?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Expats and international professionals</strong> working in Germany who need to file their first or annual
          tax declaration
        </li>
        <li><strong>Employees</strong> (Angestellte) with straightforward income situations</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Freelancers and self-employed individuals</strong> (Freiberufler und Selbstständige) with simple business
          structures
        </li>
        <li><strong>Students</strong> with part-time jobs who want to claim education-related expenses</li>
        <li><strong>Families</strong> looking to claim child benefits and related deductions</li>
        <li><strong>Anyone</strong> who wants to maximize their tax refund without hiring an expensive tax advisor</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How SmartSteuer Works</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Create Your Account:</strong> Sign up at <a
            href="https://steuererklaerung.smartsteuer.de/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener">SmartSteuer</a
          > and create your personal account.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Answer Simple Questions:</strong> The software guides you through a series of straightforward questions
          about your income, expenses, family situation, and more.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Review Your Declaration:</strong> SmartSteuer automatically generates all required tax forms based on your
          answers. You can review everything before submission.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Submit Electronically:</strong> Once you're satisfied, submit your tax declaration directly to your local
          Finanzamt via ELSTER integration.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Track Your Refund:</strong> Monitor the status of your tax declaration and receive notifications when your
          refund is processed.
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Key Features for Expats</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>English support documentation</strong> for many common questions</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Guidance on special expat situations</strong>, such as tax class optimization for married couples,
          foreign income reporting, and double taxation agreements
        </li>
        <li><strong>Help with understanding German tax terminology</strong> through clear explanations</li>
        <li><strong>Support for various visa types and residency situations</strong></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Pricing and Value</h2>
      <p>
        SmartSteuer operates on a "pay after you're satisfied" model. You can complete your entire tax declaration for
        free and only pay when you're ready to submit it to the tax office. This allows you to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Test the software without any financial commitment</li>
        <li>See your estimated refund before deciding to proceed</li>
        <li>Compare with other tax software options risk-free</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Given that the average tax refund in Germany exceeds €1,000, and many people are entitled to even larger
        refunds, the cost of SmartSteuer typically pays for itself many times over.
      </p>

      <h2>Tips for Getting the Most from SmartSteuer</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Gather all documents first:</strong> Before starting, collect your annual tax statement (Lohnsteuerbescheinigung),
          receipts for deductible expenses, and insurance documents.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Don't rush:</strong> Take your time answering questions carefully. The more accurate your information,
          the better your results.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Save as you go:</strong> SmartSteuer automatically saves your progress, so you can complete your declaration
          over several sessions.
        </li>
        <li><strong>Review everything:</strong> Before submitting, carefully review all entries to ensure accuracy.</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Keep digital copies:</strong> Download and save copies of your completed tax declaration for your records.
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Common Tax Deductions Not to Miss</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Computer and smartphone costs</strong> used for work (even partially)</li>
        <li><strong>Professional books and subscriptions</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Work clothing</strong> (if it's specific to your profession)</li>
        <li><strong>Professional memberships and union fees</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Bank account fees</strong> for salary accounts</li>
        <li><strong>Tax advisor or tax software costs</strong> from previous years</li>
        <li><strong>Job application expenses</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Dual household costs</strong> if you maintain two residences for work</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Is SmartSteuer Right for You?</h2>
      <p>While SmartSteuer is excellent for many taxpayers, certain situations may require professional tax advice:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Complex international tax situations with multiple countries</li>
        <li>Self-employment with extensive business expenses and assets</li>
        <li>Real estate investments and rental income</li>
        <li>Inheritance and gift tax issues</li>
        <li>Corporate tax matters</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        For most employees, freelancers, and expats with standard tax situations, SmartSteuer provides everything you
        need to file accurately and maximize your refund.
      </p>

      <h2>Getting Started</h2>
      <p>
        Ready to take control of your German tax declaration? Visit <a
          href="https://steuererklaerung.smartsteuer.de/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">SmartSteuer</a
        > to create your account and start your tax declaration today. Remember, you can complete everything and see your
        potential refund before committing to any payment.
      </p>
      <p>
        Filing your German taxes doesn't have to be stressful. With SmartSteuer's guided approach, intelligent deduction
        finder, and seamless ELSTER integration, you can confidently complete your Steuererklärung and get the refund
        you deserve.
      </p>

      <SmartSteuerPromo />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
